    type: "mcq",
    prompt: "A 72-year-old patient with dementia, COPD, and morbid obesity is scheduled for elective cholecystectomy. When assigning an ASA physical status classification, which combination of findings most appropriately places this patient at ASA IV rather than ASA III?",
    setup: "",
